ds JavaFileObject> diagnostic : diagnostics) {\\\\n            text.append(diagnostic.getKind())\\\\n                    .append(\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\")\\\\n                    .append(diagnostic.getMessage(Locale.ROOT))\\\\n                    .append(System.lineSeparator());\\\\n        }\\\\n        return text.toString();\\\\n    }\\\\n}\\\\n\\\"}\\n2599:[recv] {\\\"type\\\": \\\"message_end\\\", \\\"message\\\": {\\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\", \\\"content\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"thinking\\\", \\\"thinking\\\": \\\"**Planning Java source compilation with processors**\\\\n\\\\n**Configuring compile task with classpath and assertions**\\\\n\\\\n**Adding JUnit TempDir for output cleanup**\\\", \\\"thinkingSignature\\\": \\\"{\\\\\\\"id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"rs_0ccfb8ac4a0870e6016a54e8ab98b8819796eaf7a7f3061d19\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"reasoning\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\":[],\\\\\\\"encrypted_content\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"gAAAAABqVOi1sMAkTSBbGQUX-p5AS10a1yxjr6-i4EiuimkaFkcGvCu_pTuzxzgFed6vwMcgJPLUununObJC_xKuSnOis0NY5IF7ErU2n15J9ZEgBY7XVZN0oCiOpJ_fiZYMeF0PjE7W0r0B0I7O8vS3k4wuOw0p-qvc76XJ3SZS3V_ggcEbfTXGrRq_F-hE0JRE82oaTiOLt-hi6iTp0XCvg6ZOEIdA0mjVD847x276TR3hkBEAcFkgI8-_WCBxzdLegTeaL3ChAOhygn_kOscd_2Zva5JqXtunjiz_Ds4kkT4wHMOU_Ortkf_Yh-emHE7hN4QT1Bu9dBuEspXwYA8faOmdwVWJLvHyNGjRRXVrUo6CUhS0ohrYKS8vuyWMe140wHoFm3JXSRaI9-gF6UK0_pOV516Qov45VWLALe0nRwATcc2gmFntYCjCw6bH7PaKPlKmWaqOP7xeKFHk1u34whMIl_8PNZggVzlWpNo35OYHQItX5SDTXLLU4-9XylodnWorPOu2rXBm8d4dGdlsyEuhR0bs_N1JDGRyKjC118PbsVhSW-WGykzJhyQ0_LEs3EBfvPw7HEgRGEwZxZKYcIcSqYClY7sSICVPt8d3NeGcKsvDms9Q-8ia_-cVgs1NOu7HWQyNljIxcZAUvXsLY8Aoih82ESQmYj1BkDE40_4rs4pxAMbQxyoXq4Cu5vCLHbYSfYUxY-fCXWu0zwSg47_-tJQCo1hXGzkj0C1RbcctVCx3f_aYCK8bAHfX5diwM_JPas0fgqxtvK7I9OLQXlWrPPphUt9Wt6YXvI3iaNIOvd31guaQE7R4-nh_76xk6ldyZxEBofk6kT5hfTGrJdOFxpZOuvyoEL1mkgwl3zyeePOEItVET1ARiERV8RT1M3jXKvwdJhEIeQ49OtpdiKkNlDSjW6j-R6ud3sXsdWrqPzcfnu1CSQXpFQMcCrN5rv2P14d7GGqY-twYHeyJRaDZpIwcoBXuM2dFDvApCj12qETLVLWmJUszlYcDrskDiS3dENOUuGt9qrHDXOe1MVpetNYDaeCb